data.description: MAKE AN OFFER! ANY OFFER WILL BE CONSIDERED. THIS HOME HAS AN ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 3.1%. This stunning home features a unique stone and brick exterior, creating excellent curb appeal. Inside, the living room boasts high ceilings and abundant natural light. Upstairs, you'll find three bedrooms and two bathrooms, plus a versatile loft. The owner's retreat is on the main level, offering privacy and a luxurious ensuite bath. The kitchen is well-appointed with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Outside, a covered porch overlooks a greenbelt, perfect for entertaining. The community offers numerous amenities, and the property is conveniently located near Dell Diamond, Old Settler's Park, Kalahari Resort, and golf courses. Washer, dryer, and refrigerator are included.
